00:45:15.320 --> 00:45:17.430
So what are the forces
between particles--

00:45:17.430 --> 00:45:19.466
what are they going
to contribute to?

00:45:19.466 --> 00:45:20.550
Yeah, the potential.

00:45:20.550 --> 00:45:22.280
And that's going to show
