00:45:31.260 --> 00:45:32.431
or not.

00:45:32.431 --> 00:45:32.930
Good.

00:45:32.930 --> 00:45:33.718
Yeah?

00:45:33.718 --> 00:45:35.176
AUDIENCE: What's
with the particles

00:45:35.176 --> 00:45:37.303
in the state in which
