01:13:29.682 --> 01:13:32.172
OK.

01:13:32.172 --> 01:13:33.670
OK.

01:13:33.670 --> 01:13:37.010
So what does this give us?

01:13:37.010 --> 01:13:39.360
So this gives us a
couple of nice facts.

01:13:39.360 --> 01:13:48.010
So imagine-- that's
